---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import RelatedLinks from '../../components/RelatedLinks.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Breathwork Tallinn – Stress & Anxiety Relief | Hingamiskeskus"
  description="Breathwork Tallinn helps release tension, reduce stress and anxiety and bring clarity to everyday life. A natural practice for body and mind at Hingamiskeskus!"
  keywords="Teadlik vabastav hingamine, Breathwork Tallinn"
  lang="en"
  alternates={{ et: '/vabastav-hingamine', ru: '/ru/osoznannoe-dyhanie', en: '/en/breathwork' }}
>

<!-- HEADER -->
<Header active="teenused" lang="en" />

<!-- HERO SECTION (vana lehe paigutus: tekst + punktid vasakul, pilt + nupud paremal) -->
<section class="float-hero">
  <div class="float-hero__content">
    <div class="float-hero__text">
      <h1 class="float-hero__title">Breathwork in Tallinn</h1>
      <p>Conscious breathing is a breathing technique that uses continuous, uninterrupted breathing, relaxation, and focused attention.</p>
      <h2 class="float-benefits__title">Main benefits:</h2>
      <ul class="float-benefits__list">
        <li>cleanses the body of toxins</li>
        <li>clears the clutter of thoughts</li>
        <li>helps release everyday stress</li>
        <li>suppressed tensions and emotions fade away</li>
        <li>restores physical capacity</li>
        <li>improves overall well-being</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Breathing is influenced by all our thoughts and emotions. Restricting breathing is one of our defense mechanisms against negative external influences; it is the body&#39;s protective reaction to inner imbalance. With shallow breathing, we limit interaction with the external world and retreat into a confined inner world we have created for ourselves.</p>
      <p><strong>The price for a conscious breathing group session is €40. The active part lasts 1 hour, and the entire process takes approximately 2 hours and 30 minutes.</strong></p>
      <p>When breathing frees the mind, floating restores the body. Together they create deep relaxation. Come and try <a href="/en/floating" class="float-info__link">floating</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="float-hero__media">
      <img src="/images/teenus-hingamine.jpg" alt="Breathwork at Hingamiskeskus" class="float-hero__img" loading="lazy" />
      <a href="/en/book-a-session" class="float-cta__btn">BOOK A SESSION</a>
      <a href="/en/trial-package-3x" class="float-cta__promo">3X TRIAL PACKAGE SPECIAL PRICE 75€ (120€)</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SEO TEXT -->
<section class="float-seo">
  <h2 class="float-seo__heading">How does breathing affect your well-being?</h2>

  <p>Every day, we take over 20,000 breaths, adding up to more than 7 million breaths per year. Research has shown that most adults use only 10 to 20% of their full breathing capacity. That is why it is essential to be aware of how we breathe daily and to recognize the value of each breath.</p>

  <p>Since breathing has such a profound impact on both the body and mind, Rebirthing Breathwork (also known as Conscious Breathing or Connected Breathing) has gained increasing popularity worldwide. These techniques utilize continuous, uninterrupted breathing, relaxation, and focused awareness on the breath.</p>

  <p>The goal of breathwork is to release physical and mental tension through conscious, connected breathing and to awaken life energy while also cleansing the body.</p>

  <p>By speeding up or slowing down the breath, we activate both sympathetic and parasympathetic responses. Controlling the breath allows us to influence the brain and autonomic nervous system at will, literally shifting our state of consciousness. By altering our breathing rhythm, we can affect how information flows to the brain. The frequency, speed, and depth of our inhalations directly impact the brain&#39;s function and activity.</p>

  <p>Breathwork involves continuous, uninterrupted breathing, where the inhale is conscious, intentional, and deep, while the exhale is relaxed and effortless, without active control. This technique is also called connected breathing, as there are no long pauses between the inhale and exhale, connecting them into a seamless flow. Such a breathing method allows us to identify and transform limiting thoughts and past painful experiences that unconsciously influence our current behavior and mindset. By recognizing the thought patterns that hold us back, we can release them and replace them with supportive, empowering beliefs.</p>

  <p>The openness and ease of your breath reflect the lightness of your life. Through breath, we can shift patterns that restrict our breathing and embrace a life of greater flow and ease. Hingamiskeskus offers breathwork sessions in Tallinn in a safe and supportive environment where you can experience deep relaxation and inner balance.</p>
</section>

<RelatedLinks lang="en" links={[
  { href: "/en/floating", label: "Floating", desc: "Deep relaxation in Epsom salt water" },
  { href: "/en/breathwork-in-water", label: "Breathwork in water", desc: "Breathing and floating in one session" },
  { href: "/en/membership", label: "Membership", desc: "Group breathing for members, €30 per session" },
]} />

<Footer lang="en" />

</Layout>

<style>
  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    background: #fff;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .header__logo img { height: 28px; width: auto; }
  .header__right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .header__cart { color: #1d1e20; }
  .header__burger {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 4px;
  }
  .header__burger span {
    display: block;
    width: 22px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #1d1e20;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .float-hero {
    background: #f3fcff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
  }
  .float-hero__content {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-hero__text { text-align: left; }
  .float-hero__title {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }
  .float-hero__text p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .float-hero__img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  /* BENEFITS */
  .float-benefits {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-benefits__title {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 24px 0 16px;
    color: #1d1e20;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .float-benefits__list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .float-benefits__list li {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .float-info--cta {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .float-cta__btn {
    display: block;
    background: #1d1e20;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 18px 32px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .float-cta__promo {
    display: block;
    background: #1f6d85;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* HERO IMAGE */
  .float-hero-img {
    padding: 0 24px 32px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* INFO */
  .float-info {
    background: #f3fcff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-info p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .float-info p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .float-info__link {
    color: #1f6d85;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* SEO TEXT */
  .float-seo {
    background: #f3fcff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-seo p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .float-seo p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .float-seo__heading {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  /* LOCATION */
  .location {
    background: #1f6d85;
    padding: 20px 24px 24px;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .location__title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .location__address {
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .location__photo {
    width: 80%;
    max-width: 320px;
    margin: 12px auto 0;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer__main {
    background: #1f6d85;
    padding: 24px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .footer__logo {
    height: 30px;
    width: auto;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    display: block;
  }
  .footer__contact h3, .footer__hours h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .footer__contact p, .footer__hours p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .footer__hours {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .footer__social {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .footer__social a { color: #fff; }
  .footer__legal {
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    padding-top: 12px;
  }
  .footer__legal a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }

  /* DESKTOP */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .header { padding: 12px 40px; }
    .header__logo img { height: 36px; }

    .float-hero { padding: 64px 40px; }
    .float-hero__content {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 64px;
      max-width: 1200px;
    }
    .float-hero__text {
      flex: 1.15;
    }
    .float-hero__media {
      flex: 1;
      position: sticky;
      top: 100px;
    }
    .float-hero__title { font-size: 44px; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .float-hero__text p { font-size: 18px; }
    .float-benefits__list li { font-size: 16px; }
    .float-hero__img { margin-top: 0; }

    .float-seo {
      padding: 48px max(40px, calc((100% - 1100px) / 2)) 64px;
      max-width: none;
      margin: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .float-hero__title { font-size: 52px; }
    .float-hero { padding: 72px 40px; }
  }
</style>
